These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, country, disco, funk
The people have 4 different jobs:  pilot, coach, police-officer, fisherman
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, sprite, iced-tea, milk
1. the fisherman is the fan of disco##1
2. the fan of classical is on the far right##1
3. the pilot is in an odd position##4
4. the police-officer is not the fan of classical##6
5. the person drinking iced-tea is not the fisherman##6
6. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the pilot##3
7. the pilot is somewhere between the fan of disco and the coach##7
8. the person drinking 7up is between the fan of country and the fan of disco##2
9. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the fan of funk##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | disco   | funk      | country   | classical  |
| Job   | fisherman    | police-officer   | pilot | coach  |
| Beverage         | milk | 7up | iced-tea     | sprite |

