.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-2::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, july, june, january
There 4 different types of food: blueberry, cauliflower, pepper, raspberry
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, romance, mystery, sports
 1. the person eating raspberry is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person eating blueberry is in an odd position##4
 3. the person who's birthday is in june is not the person eating cauliflower##6
 4. the person who's birthday is in january is the person eating pepper##1
 5. the person eating blueberry is the person watching mystery movies##1
 6. the person eating pepper is the person watching sports movies##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1
 8. the person eating raspberry is on the left or right of the person watching romance movies##3
 9. the person who's birthday is in february is somewhere between the person eating raspberry and the person who's birthday is in june##7
10. the person watching mystery movies is on the left or right of the person eating pepper##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |      2      |     3     |   4    |
| Birthday      | july | february         | june    | january  |
| Food          | raspberry     | cauliflower | blueberry | pepper |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy     | romance     | mystery  | sports |

