.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-3::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, october, march, september
House: wooden, farmhouse, victorian, palace
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, boat, bus, taxi
1. the person driving the bus is somewhere to the right of the person driving the boat##5
2. the person who's birthday is in march is in an even position##4
3. the person driving the bus is on the far right##1
4. the wooden house is between the palace house and the person who's birthday is in march##2
5. the person who's birthday is in march is not the person driving the taxi##6
6. the person who's birthday is in march is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in october and the farmhouse house##7
7. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
8. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
9. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person driving the bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3     |      4      |
| Birthday         | september | march  | october  | november |
| House   | farmhouse   | victorian | wooden | palace     |
| Transport     | taxi    | bike     | boat     | bus         |

