3. the person traveling to rome is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1
4. the person eating kale is the person traveling to paris##1
5. the mexican is the person eating blueberry##1
6. the argentine is the person traveling to rome##1
7. the person eating blueberry is on the left or right of the person eating raspberry##3
8. the person traveling to london is somewhere between the person eating kale and the person eating cherry##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Food   | kale    | raspberry     | blueberry   | cherry      |
| Nationality   | indian    | argentine | mexican | nigerian  |
| City     | paris | rome  | london    | venice |

