3. the owner of the horse is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's hobby is writing is somewhere between the project-manager and the person who's hobby is skydiving##7
5. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the owner of the rabbit##1
6. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the far left or far right##3
7. the owner of the mouse is the person who's hobby is gardening##1
8. the designer is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |  2   |    3     |    4     |
| Hobby      | skydiving  | writing | woodworking | gardening |
| Job   | social-worker | dressmaker  | project-manager  | designer    |
| Pet           | rabbit | cat  | horse    | mouse    |

