.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-6::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: martial-arts, action, superhero, musical
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, filmmaking, magic-tricks, photography
There 4 different types of food: cherry, grapes, peach, pepper
1. the person eating pepper is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
2. the person eating pepper is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is chess##3
3. the person eating peach is somewhere to the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##5
4. the person watching superhero movies is somewhere between the person who's hobby is filmmaking and the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##7
5. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the person watching martial-arts movies##1
6. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1
7. the person watching musical movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching action movies##5
8. the person watching superhero movies is not the person eating cherry##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |     3      |      4      |
| Movie-Genre      | musical     | superhero | martial-arts        | action       |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks | chess    | filmmaking | photography |
| Food   | pepper     | grapes  | cherry    | peach   |

