3. the owner of the dog is between the owner of the goldfish and the owner of the goat##2
4. the colonial house is somewhere to the right of the craftsman house##5
5. the tiparillo-smoker is in an even position##4
6. the owner of the frog is somewhere to the left of the owner of the goldfish##5
7. the craftsman house is somewhere between the blend-smoker and the prince-smoker##7
8. the vegafina-smoker is on the left or right of the tiparillo-smoker##3
9. the ranch-style house is somewhere to the left of the owner of the dog##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |     3     |      4       |
