 1. the owner of the lizard is the cape-cod house##1
 2. the owner of the fish is on the left of the cottage house##1
 3. the owner of the rat is somewhere to the left of the cottage house##5
 4. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 5. the modern house is on the far left##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in february is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in december##5
 7. the person who's birthday is in september is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in december and the person who's birthday is in august##7
 8. the futuristic house is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in september is somewhere to the right of the owner of the lizard##5
10. the cape-cod house is on the left of the futuristic house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2       |    3    |     4     |
| House         | modern | cape-cod      | futuristic | cottage |
| Birthday   | february     | december | september  | august       |
| Pet           | rat         | lizard       | fish    | hedgehog  |

