The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, crime, horror, superhero
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, october, august, november
1. the person watching animation movies is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
2. the person watching crime movies is somewhere to the right of the person who growsbegonia##5
3. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
4. the person watching superhero movies is somewhere between the person watching animation movies and the person who growsbellflower##7
5. the person watching superhero movies is somewhere to the right of the person who growsamaryllis##5
6. the person who's birthday is in january is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in november##5
7. the person who's birthday is in august is somewhere to the right of the person watching animation movies##5
8. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
9. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who growsaconite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |    4     |
| Flower          | amaryllis  | begonia  | bellflower | aconite   |
| Movie-Genre   | animation  | superhero | crime     | horror   |
