1. the person drinking sprite is not the person driving the scooter##6
2. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the right of the person drinking water##5
3. the person watching crime movies is somewhere to the right of the person driving the scooter##5
4. the person driving the boat is not the person watching superhero movies##6
5. the person watching disaster movies is somewhere to the right of the person drinking juice##5
6. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
7. the person watching horror movies is somewhere between the person drinking water and the person driving the snowmobile##7
8. the person driving the scooter is not the person watching crime movies##6
9. the person drinking water is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3      |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero      | horror | disaster  | crime    |
| Beverage         | water | juice  | coffee | sprite    |
| Transport     | jet-ski       | boat      | scooter    | snowmobile |

