4. the person drinking fanta is between the indonesian and the person who's birthday is in may##2
5. the nigerian is not the person drinking almond-milk##6
6. the person who's birthday is in february is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in june##5
7. the person who's birthday is in may is the mexican##1
8. the indonesian is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in february##3
9. the nigerian is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in june and the person drinking soy-milk##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |     3      |   4    |
