The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, roller, skateboard, tram
 1. the person who likes azure is somewhere to the left of the person driving the roller##5
 2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
 3. the person driving the tram is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person driving the skateboard is between the person who likes pink and the person who likes grey##2
 5. the person driving the helicopter is somewhere to the right of the person who likes black##5
 6. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##5
 7. the person who likes pink is not the person who's hobby is woodworking##6
 8. the person driving the helicopter is somewhere between the person who's hobby is collecting and the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##7
 9. the person who likes azure is somewhere to the left of the person who likes grey##5
10. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
11. the person who likes azure is between the person who likes grey and the person who likes pink##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3      |    4     |
| Hobby      | rock-climbing | singing     | woodworking      | collecting     |
| Color   | black  | pink   | azure   | grey |
| Transport     | tram     | helicopter | skateboard | roller   |

